snippet.title: Experience the Next Generation of Competition in Rocket League Season 18
snippet.description: Buckle up and blast off to the near future in Rocket League Season 18 starting March 14! Drift into the all-new Futura Garden Arena and experience the next generation of competition. https://rl.gg/season-18
